headline: Robinhood Chain And Venture Fund Reshape Access To Crypto And Private Markets
summary: Robinhood Markets (NasdaqGS:HOOD) has launched Robinhood Chain, its own blockchain designed to support crypto trading and tokenized assets. The company also introduced Robinhood Ventures Fund I, a vehicle intended to give retail investors access to private companies. These moves extend Robinhood’s reach beyond brokerage services into blockchain infrastructure and retail focused venture investing. Robinhood, best known for its app based stock and crypto trading, is pushing further into...

headline: Kueski Appoints Pablo Baragiola, Former Robinhood, Nubank and Capital One Executive, as Vice President of Fraud
summary: MEXICO CITY, February 26, 2026--Kueski, one of the largest buy now, pay later (BNPL) and online consumer lenders in Latin America, today announced the appointment of Pablo Baragiola as Vice President of Fraud. The appointment reflects Kueski’s continued focus on strengthening core platform capabilities as it scales one of the most widely used digital financial ecosystems in Mexico.
